# Config-as-Code Export Bundle

Generated by **clickopstocaac** for migration or same-cluster config-as-code.

## Quick Apply

```bash
export TARGET_AAP_URL=https://aap-gateway.example.com
export TARGET_AAP_TOKEN=<gateway-oauth-token>
ansible-galaxy collection install -r requirements.yml
../../scripts/apply.sh --bundle . --check
../../scripts/apply.sh --bundle .
```

Phased migration apply:

```bash
../../scripts/apply.sh --bundle . --phase organizations --check
../../scripts/apply.sh --bundle . --phase credentials,projects,job_templates
```

